@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
title Activity Diagram - Gan CLO voi Rubric qua Rubric Matrix

|Main Lecturer|
start
:Mo man hinh Rubric Matrix;
:Bam "Ma tran moi" hoac sua ma tran;

|Frontend (React)|
:Tai danh sach CLO va rubric;
:Mo RubricMatrixEditor;

|Main Lecturer|
:Chon rubric nen;
:Them / xoa tieu chi;
:Gan CLO cho tung tieu chi;
:Them cac muc danh gia (level);
:Nhap diem so, thu tu, mo ta cho tung level;
:Bam "Xem truoc" neu can;

|Frontend (React)|
:Tinh tong trong so;
:Dem so criteria da gan CLO;
:Dem so criteria co level;
:Hien validation cards;

if (Tong trong so = 100%\nva tat ca criteria da gan CLO\nva deu co level?) then (No)
  |Main Lecturer|
  :Dieu chinh lai thong tin ma tran;
  stop
else (Yes)
endif

|Main Lecturer|
:Bam "Luu ma tran";

|Frontend (React)|
:Dong goi payload RubricMatrixRequest;
:POST /api/v1/rubric-service/rubric-matrices;

|Backend (Rubric Service)|
:RubricMatrixController nhan request;
:RubricMatrixService.updateMatrix(...);
:Tim rubric theo id,\nneu chua co thi khoi tao moi;
:Cap nhat ten, mo ta rubric;
:Lap qua tung criterion;
:Cap nhat ten, trong so, cloId;
:Tao / cap nhat cac level cua criterion;
:Xoa lien ket cu va gan tap criteria moi;
:Luu rubric vao database;
:Tra ve true;

|Frontend (React)|
:Dong editor;
:Co the tai lai danh sach matrix;

|Main Lecturer|
:Xem matrix da cap nhat;
stop
@enduml
